claim.claim-text:
A cap assembly (100, 200) for a lithium ion secondary battery (1000, 2000), comprising:
a cap plate (30, 97) comprising a supporting portion (31, 971) and a safety film (32, 972) positioned in the supporting portion (31, 971), the safety film (32, 972) defining safety grooves (33, 973), the safety film (31, 971) be capable of break down along the safety grooves (33, 973);
a leakproof film (20, 98) attached on the supporting portion (31, 971), the leakproof film (20, 98) being made of a material with high temperature resistance and elasticity properties; and a cap cover (10, 99) attached on the leakproof film (20, 98).
